  "title": "Warehouse Assistant [Sports Equipment] - East, 5 Days Work",
  "description": "<p><strong>Summary:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Location: East</p></li><li><p>Industry: Sports Equipment</p></li><li><p>5 days work, Mon - Fri</p></li></ul><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Loading and unloading of goods.</p></li><li><p>Picking, packing, labelling, wrapping of products.</p></li><li><p>Ascertain amount of goods released and received are correct.</p></li><li><p>Perform general housekeeping.</p></li><li><p>Perform stock take periodically and maintain stock level.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Possessing a forklift license will be an advantage (not mandatory).</p></li><li><p>Candidates with 1–2 years of relevant experience will have an added advantage.</p></li></ul><p><br /><br />To Apply, kindly click on the <strong>\"APPLY NOW\"</strong> button</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>Staffking Pte Ltd (20C0358) | Boo Seng Hong (R25129172)</p>",
